HEADWORD: Displode
<hw>Dis*plode"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To burst with a loud report;
to explode.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Disploding</xex> engines.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Young.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
